reviewText: very relaxing looks great on the big screen what an artist.
Love Thomas Kikade and his works of art!
I would definitely recommend this to anyone who enjoys the Thomas Kinkade paintings.  What a lovely way to fill a widescreen tv screen.

i am truly a fan of his work. i have collected the paintings,cd's,dvd's,figurines and the calendars. i see alot of his work at my jod(fedex).and his spiritual side is fantastic. i wish him nothing but God's blessings.
